OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,FLong delays coupled with extreme heat
OL,7,Fthis summer could create a
OL,8,F"humanitarian crisis" at the Port of
OL,9,FDover, a Kent MP has warned.
OL,11,FSir Roger Gale said operators would be
OL,12,Fleft facing a "very serious
OL,13,Fsituation", if a worst case prediction
OL,14,Fof 12 hour queues materialises.
OL,16,FThe MP for Herne Bay and Sandwich's
OL,17,Fcomments come less than a week away
OL,18,Ffrom when more than 14 million
OL,19,Fmotorists are expected to embark on
OL,20,Ftheir summer holidays.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
