FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,FIt also comes at a time when the
OL,7,FEuropean Union's (EU) new Entry/Exit
OL,8,FSystem (EES) is causing huge delays
OL,9,Ffor people hoping to enter the
OL,10,FSchengen Area.
OL,12,F"Potentially we're facing a
OL,13,Fhumanitarian disaster," Sir Roger told
OL,14,FITV Meridian.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
