OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,F" I don't say that lightly. Twelve
OL,7,Fhours in the heat, throughout the day,
OL,8,Fin July (and) August with children,
OL,9,Felderly people, animals without
OL,10,Flavatory facilities, possibly without
OL,11,Fwater, we are talking about heart
OL,12,Fattacks.
OL,14,F"We're talking about very serious
OL,15,Fissues indeed."
OL,26,@pD@IpmpD@Mpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
