PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,FThe EES system, which was rolled out
OL,7,Ffully in April, involves people from
OL,8,Fthird-party countries, such as the UK,
OL,9,Fhaving their fingerprints registered
OL,10,Fand photograph taken to enter the
OL,11,FSchengen Area - which consists of 29
OL,12,FEuropean countries, mainly in the bloc.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
