OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,FFor most UK travellers, the process is
OL,7,Fdone at foreign airports, but it's
OL,8,Falso carried out at the Port of Dover,
OL,9,FEurotunnel's Folkestone terminal and
OL,10,FLondon St Pancras railway station.
OL,12,FMany passengers have spent hours stuck
OL,13,Fin EES queues, since the system was
OL,14,Fintroduced.
OL,16,FPort of Dover CEO Doug Bannister
OL,17,Fdefended his organisation's role in
OL,18,Fthe disruption, saying "we have done
OL,19,Feverything we can".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "I don't know that
OL,7,Fanybody's to blame, but what we are
OL,8,Fwaiting on is for the technology to
OL,9,Fget activated so that we can open up
OL,10,Fthe site."
OL,12,FHome Office minister Alex Norris has
OL,13,Fpreviously said that the government
OL,14,Fhas pushed "very heavily" for the
OL,15,Fmovement of people to be given
OL,16,Fprecedence over compliance with EES.
OL,18,FBut the EU has rejected calls from
OL,19,Fairline and airport groups to suspend
OL,20,Fit until September.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
