OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,FPassengers have instead been urged to
OL,7,Fallow for extra time to avoid missing
OL,8,Ftheir flights back home.
OL,10,FTravel Journalist Lisa Francesca Nand
OL,11,Fsaid the new system "just makes sense"
OL,12,Fand will "become smoother" over time.
OL,14,F"I know it's annoying or frustrating,
OL,15,Fif you're stuck in a queue, but in the
OL,16,Flong term this makes so much sense,"
OL,17,Fshe told ITV Meridian.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
