OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784045920
OL,3,CBorder check delays and extreme heat
OL,4,Cpose 'crisis' risk at port, MP warns
OL,6,FShe added: "It's a completely old
OL,7,Ffashioned way now to have your
OL,8,Fpassports stamped, much as we all love
OL,9,Flooking at the stamps in our
OL,10,Fpassports."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
